Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.98,0:01:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向全岛民通告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.94,0:01:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在全岛的设施由我们人类军掌管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.59,0:01:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的目的是视察并接管此岛的全部区域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.98,0:01:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以承诺不对岛屿加以危害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.38,0:01:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我们的作战目的不仅于此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.89,0:01:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.92,0:01:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛被占领了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.27,0:01:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸妈妈不要紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.82,0:02:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.24,0:02:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆 我们会怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.55,0:02:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.39,0:02:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 忍耐一下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.48,0:02:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在岛屿检查完毕之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.13,0:02:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你们在这里多呆一会儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.20,0:02:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食物什么的就要准备好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.44,0:02:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续关心岛民 不要怠慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.38,0:02:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.25,0:02:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有向海岸传达立刻找出核
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.01,0:02:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服的座椅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.58,0:02:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核到底在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.67,0:02:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是第几次抽到鬼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.10,0:02:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不记得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.94,0:02:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭还没好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.95,0:02:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不让我们出战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.76,0:03:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此简单的就将岛交出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.10,0:03:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沟口先生他们回来的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.37,0:03:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无颜面对一骑 吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.23,0:03:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.99,0:03:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以同人类战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.52,0:03:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论发生什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.59,0:03:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦发生流血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.78,0:03:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑回来之时痛苦的会是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.59,0:03:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你战斗过吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.88,0:03:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不堪回首啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.36,0:03:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一一骑为了人类军而战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.12,0:03:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能救他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.43,0:03:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会救的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.93,0:03:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.35,0:03:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你相信一骑吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.33,0:03:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不过什么也没跟我说就跑出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.43,0:03:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底是不是信任我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.23,0:03:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话 我没什么信心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.30,0:03:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那和我一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.11,0:03:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第15话 记忆～呼喊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.58,0:04:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李利克斯尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.25,0:04:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去追那部机体噢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.68,0:04:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.11,0:04:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是没能帮上什么忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.46,0:04:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那样的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.11,0:04:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐能在最后关头陪伴身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.61,0:04:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮了洋治大忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.60,0:04:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.80,0:04:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 这次要去见一骑了噢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.57,0:04:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.41,0:04:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我奉日野洋治之命来将赛因号交给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.74,0:04:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛因号 日野先生呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.20,0:04:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日野洋治已经死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.61,0:04:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾等不能容忍我有更多的分歧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.31,0:04:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 妈妈 是妈妈吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.69,0:05:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁红音已经死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.39,0:05:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是被你们称作菲斯特姆的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.37,0:05:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是把核之器交给你这个阿尔比斯之子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.84,0:05:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘上去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.25,0:05:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.92,0:05:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.23,0:05:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最后还有句要传达吾等的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.82,0:05:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾等限制了你的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.74,0:05:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾等理解人类的个性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.69,0:05:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾等不能理解你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.04,0:05:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你自己要拒绝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.88,0:05:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是吾等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.62,0:05:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但为什么还要交谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.82,0:05:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经放弃了分歧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.36,0:05:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已是你的一部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.17,0:05:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么还要谈话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.07,0:06:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体的感觉完全不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.76,0:06:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.97,0:06:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾等应该已合为一体还能看见对方的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.54,0:06:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以我的方式存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.10,0:06:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你以自己的方式存在一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.93,0:06:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我一定要传达给吾等的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.80,0:06:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾等不承认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.25,0:06:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.34,0:06:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.82,0:06:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把妈妈吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.84,0:07:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.13,0:07:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 看那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.29,0:07:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那部机体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.54,0:07:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.30,0:08:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.35,0:08:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.88,0:08:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.71,0:08:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.01,0:08:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是还没有出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.22,0:08:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让核转生的话现在才开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.73,0:08:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.36,0:09:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.67,0:09:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈生病了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.18,0:09:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.22,0:09:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸..爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.74,0:09:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.52,0:09:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.19,0:09:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士的眼睛怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.89,0:09:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是一个人玩的时候摔了一跤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.17,0:09:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.41,0:09:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.55,0:09:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊 好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.42,0:09:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我干的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.64,0:09:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士的左眼很难恢复了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.02,0:09:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么重的伤 真的是摔伤的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.31,0:09:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.83,0:09:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 你没说是我做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.53,0:09:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.30,0:10:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为这样一直以来都没能向你道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.16,0:10:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.35,0:10:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能行的话 我会去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.01,0:10:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是那个伤使你无法驾驶法弗尼尔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.51,0:10:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么不怪我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.94,0:10:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不说是我做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.34,0:10:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我逃避了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.90,0:10:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那个时候我丢下你逃走了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.68,0:10:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好怕 好怕那个时候伤害了你的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.17,0:10:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我逃避了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.84,0:10:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你生我气了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.08,0:10:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨我了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.81,0:10:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以叫我战斗直至战死是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.10,0:10:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.68,0:10:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直就想消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.64,0:10:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这种人消失了就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.79,0:10:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少要向你道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.27,0:10:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次的伤痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.74,0:10:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.40,0:11:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个核为了唤醒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.40,0:11:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使你向总士做了那样的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.97,0:11:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的伤痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.27,0:11:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己存在的证明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.00,0:11:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士感谢一骑你了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.67,0:11:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.22,0:11:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么伤害了总士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.85,0:11:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.25,0:11:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来唤起你的记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.21,0:11:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.42,0:11:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.85,0:12:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士 为什么你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.59,0:12:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.51,0:12:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是合体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.64,0:12:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.52,0:12:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合体吧 一骑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.07,0:12:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的都被吞噬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.51,0:12:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋治那家伙到底做出了什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.51,0:12:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑在那里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.82,0:12:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.37,0:13:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 连这里都想吞了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.38,0:13:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初大家都是同体的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.04,0:13:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既大又深的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.36,0:13:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那里出来后大家就分开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.07,0:13:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为自己 成为人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.17,0:13:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一来语言诞生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.82,0:13:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合为一体且没有旁骛的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.28,0:13:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有回到那里去的渴望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.62,0:13:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会有新的发现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.76,0:13:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为如果不知道自己在哪儿 也不会有回归的渴望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.63,0:13:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是产生许多邂逅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.60,0:13:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在对于我们来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.60,0:13:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相伤害才有这样的可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.64,0:13:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 那是什么童话吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.99,0:13:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 宇宙和我们的童话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.37,0:13:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神赐予了我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.10,0:14:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既高兴又哀伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.16,0:14:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是只属于我们的物语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.40,0:14:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这叫同化现象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.58,0:14:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是印在我们体内的通往遥远之地的回归之路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.28,0:14:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回归之路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.73,0:14:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸说附身印记依存于我们的遗传因子上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.80,0:14:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说我是为了保护岛上的核而活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.08,0:14:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以为了自己或别人而活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.50,0:14:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.37,0:14:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从一开始就不存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.33,0:14:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想回到能和你合为一体的地方去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.29,0:14:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.57,0:14:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士 你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.08,0:14:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择同化现象的虽然只有一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.74,0:14:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还有其他方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.81,0:14:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们体内的回归之路和未来之路都有印记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.57,0:14:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你选择哪一方 一骑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.91,0:15:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.27,0:15:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.87,0:15:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.60,0:15:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是想消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.64,0:15:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想和总士再交谈一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.15,0:15:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.32,0:15:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你选择留在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.14,0:15:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.23,0:15:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交谈是作为自己作为人类的证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.99,0:15:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.39,0:15:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.58,0:15:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我指示了核应该去的方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.17,0:15:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.92,0:15:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是极限了 逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.34,0:15:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 一骑可能还在下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.94,0:15:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.41,0:15:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.07,0:15:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.21,0:16:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然自食了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.95,0:16:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.12,0:16:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.84,0:16:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会在这儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.90,0:16:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.84,0:16:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天会叫的只有金龟子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.13,0:17:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想捉鍬形虫 在傍晚设陷阱比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.92,0:17:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后然后呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.19,0:17:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢什么陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.12,0:17:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到些白天会分泌树汁的树 为了晚上也能走制作出地图
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.98,0:17:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生物部的那些家伙只会做些蹩脚的陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.67,0:17:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是让我找到了就全埋到土里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.98,0:17:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过被发现就要挨骂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.45,0:17:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真温柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.75,0:17:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调查完成后再聊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.68,0:17:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来 你的名字是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.52,0:17:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.24,0:17:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.55,0:17:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.31,0:17:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.13,0:17:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不给的话过会儿就没机会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.36,0:17:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真麻烦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.45,0:17:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.80,0:17:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里干吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.03,0:18:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 在这种地方不要把名字叫那么响
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.98,0:18:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是你叫我叫你名字的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.93,0:18:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.77,0:18:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.05,0:18:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏了那么个大家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.41,0:18:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没别的了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.91,0:18:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道了 你们自己调查一下怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.94,0:18:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.12,0:18:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以回家去了吗 还有原稿的上色没完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.73,0:18:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛上的防御系统尚能使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.65,0:18:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说明核还留在这个岛上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.00,0:18:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 的确如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.06,0:18:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要注意一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.63,0:18:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始对敌人的迎击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.89,0:18:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多余的人员先回避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.38,0:18:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要扯我们的后腿 迅速展开搜查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.44,0:18:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的行动都向本部汇报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.58,0:18:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了你我们查到了不少好东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.27,0:18:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向光博先生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.64,0:18:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认到一架菲斯特姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.24,0:18:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离120
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.45,0:19:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从西南方向向龙宫岛接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.77,0:19:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是试验诺顿模型的好机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.82,0:19:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让这些人驾驶法弗尼尔？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.54,0:19:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没做过意识反应测试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.90,0:19:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危险的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.13,0:19:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.24,0:19:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺顿模型数据已做过调整
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.80,0:19:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们是我军的精英
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.14,0:19:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻让她们驾驶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.82,0:19:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.09,0:19:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 让我进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.77,0:19:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 这里面未经许可禁止进入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.28,0:19:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们以为你们能用好那个CDC吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.19,0:19:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.20,0:19:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来负责
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.17,0:19:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.07,0:19:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.39,0:19:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过的好吗 弓子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.73,0:19:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.93,0:19:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是哪位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.38,0:19:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击了 TRIBBLE6号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.98,0:19:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.03,0:19:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 弓子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.86,0:19:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不认识你 别跟着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.64,0:20:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人是什么人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.36,0:20:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.98,0:20:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.44,0:20:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的在这里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.77,0:20:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在啊 在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.62,0:20:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.48,0:20:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.86,0:20:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城他在岛上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.40,0:20:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定在等着一骑的消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.15,0:20:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在岛外见到的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.44,0:21:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.64,0:21:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话就能了解他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.60,0:21:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是害怕战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.51,0:21:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我真的怕自己会消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.75,0:21:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白一骑的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.41,0:21:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来想像我这种人还是消失了好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.49,0:21:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.55,0:21:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去再谈一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.93,0:21:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不这样的话 也许自己和对方都会消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.65,0:21:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以多谈几次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.57,0:21:52.95,1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样伤感可不像我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.38,0:22:02.03,1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好没事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.73,0:22:04.93,1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沟口先生知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.21,0:22:07.03,1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.60,0:22:10.67,1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的妈妈是怎么死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.32,0:22:15.80,1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红音为了保护史彦被菲斯特姆杀害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.30,0:22:18.85,1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那个时候也在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.48,0:22:20.25,1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.82,0:22:23.14,1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以爸爸说是自己的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.40,0:22:24.36,1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.42,0:22:27.66,1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.12,0:22:30.37,1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就安心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.05,0:22:34.88,1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 回去吧 回你的故乡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.21,0:22:37.48,1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和回去的意义有点不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.71,0:22:43.38,1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本什么都不知道时无法了解那岛上的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.14,0:22:51.67,1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许比起回去 龙宫岛是我不得不去的地方呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.92,0:22:55.25,1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前也有人说过相似的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.38,0:22:58.99,1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再像以前那样想了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.60,0:23:02.55,1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么一定要保护自己的岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.27,0:23:05.57,1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那难道是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.83,0:23:08.61,1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.69,0:23:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面目全非的岛屿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.75,0:23:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断受伤的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.93,0:23:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 她面对天空的那番话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.66,0:23:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回  苍穹的Fafnir  第十六话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.72,0:23:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.07,0:23:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里吗


